    "chemicalDescription": [
      "sr-(Oligopeptide-249 sh-Polypeptide-11) is a single chain recombinant peptide produced by fermentation in E. coli. The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the genes from Oligopeptide-249 and sh-Polypeptide-11. The fusion peptide contains 152 amino acids which may contain disulfide bonds and/or glycosylation, and consists of the proper sequence from the 20 standard amino acids."
